    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the instability part, but some people argue that if the west hadn't stepped in, it would've been way worse, like a genocidal regime staying in power. does that change the \"failure\" label at all or does the lack of stability just outweigh everything else?",
      "source": "evaluator"
